But she reacts like that.

125
00:06:09,270 --> 00:06:10,110
Well...

126
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:12,510
That's good.

127
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,160
Although we're married,

128
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,560
(The Book of Songs)
my life

129
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:17,120
