of my appearance?

131
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:30,390
Your Highness, you have
flawless features.

132
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:32,840
Have I been popular

133
00:06:33,310 --> 00:06:34,150
with women

134
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,630
these years?

135
00:06:36,390 --> 00:06:37,630
No doubt.

136
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,630
But Her Highness
doesn't care about this.

137
00:06:49,950 --> 00:06:50,790
Mingshu,

138
00:06:52,510 --> 00:06:53,800
