145
00:07:08,190 --> 00:07:09,600
My mother and buddy

146
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,070
love me.

147
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,320
What about you?

148
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,830
Your family is wealthy.

149
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,750
You life must be
easy and happy.

150
00:07:17,390 --> 00:07:19,600
My father has been
strict with me.

151
00:07:20,310 --> 00:07:22,000
He's arranged everything
for me.

152
00:07:22,830 --> 00:07:24,560
I've never finished a thing

153
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:25,560
at my will.

154
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,630
That explains why

155
00:07:28,950 --> 00:07:29,870
I always overthink

156
00:07:29,870 --> 00:07:31,000
before I act.

157
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,430
I can't be as spontaneous
as you.

158
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,390
So I envy you a lot.

159
00:07:42,950 --> 00:07:43,790
Mingshu?

160
