be benefited?"

164
00:08:49,870 --> 00:08:50,840
The officials asked,

165
00:08:50,930 --> 00:08:52,240
"How can my family
be benefited?"

166
00:08:52,420 --> 00:08:53,750
Scholars and
common folks asked,

167
00:08:53,750 --> 00:08:55,000
"How can I myself
be benefited?"

168
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:57,080
